"2020-07-03T02:34:16.000Z","msg":"你個牌呃返嚟㗎？屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nVHIS都全球保障啦，返去睇清楚啲terms先上嚟留tg搵食"},{"pid":"4365989b3c2b02cf946c5e645336107242cb8e9f","tid":2091800,"uid":11462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a514a6bc50fd1b42bfd83679a2256edc5c48c82d","tid":2091800,"uid":360471,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:54:30.000Z","msg":"香港醫療單主要分三種<br />\n<br />\n1. 基本醫療<br />\n (例如基本VHIS，每項目sub-limit，有得on top買額外醫療保障SMM) <br />\n呢種單大部份全球保障，但plan design依香港收費為參考，去到外國有機會唔夠用<br />\n<br />\n2. Local 半High-End<br />\n呢種單多數無項目限額，lump sum 幾百萬到幾千萬限額<br />\n但半High-End意思就係只保特定地區同指定房級<br />\n (例如只限亞洲+半私家房) <br />\n只有緊急情況先可以係域外使用(甚至唔得)，可能索償方面有調整<br />\n<br />\n3. Local High-End<br />\n都係無項目限額，去到私家房級別同環球保障(或美國除外)<br />\n<br />\n但前提係，保費會因居住地不同而改變，移民一定要通知保險公司。"},{"pid":"829f22a8518eb6431424c8b85083dc96ba57e22b","tid":2091800,"uid":84208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb2a67e837acf6fbb93f8a4fbca1fc6ba6b8513c","tid":2091800,"uid":11462,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18754caf26d770437bad99c94a9ec53bdd658878","tid":2091800,"uid":84208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:02:44.000Z","msg":"有冇呢方面巴打可以討論下<br />\n<br />\n以我所知香港的保險係包全球，夠唔夠cover 呢<br />\n<br />\n但自願醫保，如果移左民，又會變左點呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:23:51.000Z","msg":"保費跟你居住地有關 你依家買緊既保費係以你係香港為原居地而定<br />\n如果長居外地多過180日/一年，就會當你非常居香港加地域保費<br />\n<br />\n我建議買真international (Aetna, April, Bupa Global, NowHealth)嗰種而唔係香港既環球保障"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:54:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd1eebc1bf06678c8bfb25e22463d8c40b5ee2c","tid":2091800,"uid":84208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"自願醫保會點<br />\n<br />\n算唔算係香港身份先買得<br />\n<br />\n無左個身份會唔會無左張單"},{"pid":"fcab519adbcef0fe0998b9812d48117c42b817cd","tid":2091800,"uid":360471,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b634eef0e0dc221953a731a0577cc0c6a865b975","tid":2091800,"uid":360471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:40:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3006860e8384678fd6d41c770525577c8be8b56a","tid":2091800,"uid":11462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fcab519adbcef0fe0998b9812d48117c42b817cd","tid":2091800,"uid":360471,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b42476b122f4425bac6bae57a2a08d517c93df78","tid":2091800,"uid":11462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a514a6bc50fd1b42bfd83679a2256edc5c48c82d","tid":2091800,"uid":360471,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:34:16.000Z","msg":"你個牌呃返嚟㗎？屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nVHIS都全球保障啦，返去睇清楚啲terms先上嚟留tg搵食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:41:32.000Z","msg":"CEO plan? 做AIA啊？ 你淨係識一張Product所以大部份淨係包亞洲？唔係啊話<br />\n<br />\n就拎AIA啲VHIS嚟計<br />\n<br />\nVHIS Standard <br />\n「保障地域範圍 <br />\n除本第六部分第3(1)節的精神科治療外，本條款及保障內所有保障均全球適用。」\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000 \u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000 \u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000 \u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000 \u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000<br />\n<br />\nVHIS Flexi<br />\n「保障地域範圍 <br />\n除本第六部分第3(1)節的精神科治療外，本條款及保障內所有保障均全球適用。」<br />\n<br />\nVHIS 尊尚<br />\n「保障地域範圍 <br />\n除本第六部分第3(1)節的精神科治療外，本條款及保障必須受本條款及保障賠償限制批註所列明的地域範圍限制所規限。」<br />\n<br />\n\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000 \u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000<br />\n\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000「地域範圍限制<br />\n任何於亞洲以外接受的非急症治療，其應付賠償將受標準計劃保障表的賠償限額所規限，」<br />\n<br />\n你個人角度覺得唔包全球，咁就代表張單唔Operative? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海外唔夠Cover同唔Cover係完全唔同既嘢，concept錯到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d496fdc660f6c3f65c2c7bf1b59fdf59abcd233","tid":2091800,"uid":360949,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T12:39:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ffb5b9c6a0a5558d137fdd23eb223ec051fa343","tid":2091800,"uid":360471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T23:21:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"354c6d27c823b95ba81cf3b75ae0cbd030eceb2f","tid":2091800,"uid":360471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T23:29:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"160d17df936025eb797bfb1dfbc03f26c31e836d","tid":2091800,"uid":164491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e534ce71df90ad1c60e6a22e00e4c958db193c","tid":2091800,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18754caf26d770437bad99c94a9ec53bdd658878","tid":2091800,"uid":84208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:02:44.000Z","msg":"有冇呢方面巴打可以討論下<br />\n<br />\n以我所知香港的保險係包全球，夠唔夠cover 呢<br />\n<br />\n但自願醫保，如果移左民，又會變左點呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:26:08.000Z","msg":"Ching 係咪唔知咩叫 NHS<br />\n洗鬼保險?"},{"pi